/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/10/UCL-logo-small-use-blk-300x88.jpg" width="201" height="59" /></a><a href="http://research.micropasts.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/10/bmlogo_print.png"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-55" alt="bmlogo_print" src="http://research.micropasts.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/10/bmlogo_print-300x106.png" width="173" height="61" /></a><a href="http://research.micropasts.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/10/portable_antiquities_scheme_logo.jpg"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-58" alt="portable_antiquities_scheme_logo" src="http://research.micropasts.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/10/portable_antiquities_scheme_logo.jpg" width="153" height="75" /></a>', 'About the project', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-18 17:21:22', '2013-10-18 17:21:22', '', 26, 'http://research.micropasts.org/2013/10/18/26-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
